import React from "react"; function Intro() { return (

Hi there, and welcome to
Quietly Thriving.

My name is Natascha Henriksen and I am a mindset + business coach for introverted women.

Join my Community on Facebook to receive weekly updates, reminders, general info......

Go to Facebook

If you are interested in knowing more on how to work with me, you can book a first free 30 minutes call.
I can't wait to meet you.

Book a meeting

Quietly thriving is all about taking the power into your own hands – all in your pace. No competition, no need for attention, no need to show the whole world what you’re doing, no deadline, no pressure. It’s just about YOU! Thank you for being here!

); } export default Intro;
